               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I am guilty of changing the half-sovereign, not knowing it was bad. It does not stand to reason that I should go into a house close to where I have lived twenty-five years, and where I am always in the habit of going backwards and forwards every day.</p>
